name: CORSINA PRETTY
description: Feel over the moon in this romantic bra by Triumph. A staple for every woman's lingerie, the nonwired bra made from jaquard and soft cotton, provides extra Triumph comfort for a great value.

name: SLOGGI 24/7 MICROFIBRE
description: Update your everyday essentials with this super comfy bra from the 24/7 Microfibre series by sloggi. Its long and well proven cup cut offers best wearing feeling while the stretchy and light fabric is comfy on your skin.

name: CYNTHIA
description: Feel unbeatable confidence in the Triumph Cynthia series of shapewear. This elegant bodyshaper by Triumph is made from a blend of materials that is designed for perfect fit and optimal shaping effects.

name: TRIACTION HYBRID LITE
description: Good if a sports bra is as light and flexible like the one from the Triumph triaction Hybrid Lite series and nevertheless offers maximum support.

name: MODERN FINESSE
description: This softly padded bra of the Triumph Modern Finesse series offers great comfort and pure elegance for every day.

name: TRUE SHAPE SENSATION
description: The padded bra from the True Shape Sensation series is part of a new generation of elegant and intelligent shapewear created by Triumph.

name: SEXY ANGEL SPOTLIGHT
description: Triumph created with its Sexy Angel Spotlight series a feminine line, which convinces you with its fine quality and delicate lace embellishments.

name: SLOGGI ZERO LACE
description: This lace short from the ZERO Lace serieS by sloggi feels like a second skin. Super flat and soft lace makes it highly comfortable to wear without being visible under tight clothes.

name: PEONY FLORALE
description: Fulfil your lingerie dreams with this richly decorated and sophisticated bra from the Peony Florale series giving a naturally rounded and superbly supported shape.

name: PEONY FLORALE
description: Update your lingerie edit with elegance, femininity and a touch of romantic flowers. This bra from the Peony Florale series by Triumph definitely has it all. Optimal, wireless support combined with exclusive design promise to fulfil all lingerie dreams.

name: BEAUTY-FULL ESSENTIAL
description: Sporty can be so feminine! Like with this t-shirt bra from the Beauty-Full Essential series by Triumph.

name: BEAUTY-FULL ESSENTIAL
description: Experience the feminine and timeless Beauty-Full series by Triumph and experience this beautiful bra, which offers optimal support and perfect fit.

name: TRIACTION WELLNESS
description: Unwind, take a deep breath and feel your body - not your underwear. This unwired sports bra from the Studio-Wellness series by Triumph is so light you won't feel it, offering support and comfort.

name: AMOURETTE 300
description: This delicate and feminine bra with lace is from the Triumph Amourette 300 series and is slightly padded and perfect for wearing under elegant t-shirts or glamorous silk tops.

name: TRIACTION MAGIC MOTION
description: The sports bra from the triaction Magic Motion series by Triumph is a true sensation. The Magic Wire Push up technology has found its way to the gym, offering freedom of movement and maximum support at the same time. Now that really sounds magical.

name: DREAM SPOTLIGHT
description: The playful Dream Spotlight series excites with a stylish everyday look extra for style conscious women. The romantic bra is the perfect proof.

name: MODERN BEAUTY
description: Combining a feminine look and a natural touch, especially made for fuller sizes, this wired bra from the Modern Beauty series by Triumph meets all needs. Neutral colours keep cool and invisible under clothing while pretty embroidery adds that extra touch.

name: BEAUTY-FULL DARLING
description: An absolutely sensual t-shirt bra from the Triumph Beauty-Full Darling  series. Modern design turns into an absolute eye-catcher with oriental-style lace ornaments.

name: BEAUTY-FULL ESSENTIAL
description: Smooth satin and feminine lace together with its extra soft feel make this bra from the Beauty-Full series by Triumph an absolute must-have. So good it's even invisible under clothes.

name: COOL SENSATION
description: Slim your silhouette and feel fresher all day long in this Triumph shapewear bodysuit with cooling effect fabric. What's more, the seamless edging allows for an invisible fit under clothes. The combination of cosy knit and smooth functional lace give this moulded cup, bodysuit by Triumph Shape Sensation a stellar look.

name: MODERN FINESSE
description: The bra from the Modern Finesse series by Triumph is a chic addition to any lingerie drawer. Made from delicate lace guaranteeing perfect fit makes it a true gem.

name: DREAM SPOTLIGHT
description: You are searching for that one bra to give you that absolute wow-feeling? Take a closer look at the push-up miracle from the Dream Spotlight series by Triumph and enjoy a stylish everyday favourite.

name: WILD ROSE FLORALE
description: Add impeccable elegance to your ensembles with this bra so romantic you'll be swept off your feet. This bra from the Wild Rose Florale series by Triumph creates a breath-taking cleavage without adding extra volume. What more could one ask for?
